data.description: ****Offering $5,000 in concessions****  Great 3/2/2 family home in the NW Lubbock neighborhood of Westchester Park. This home offers a semi-open layout in the living, kitchen, and dining areas with built-in surround sound in the living room and back porch, built-in bookshelves in the living room and office, a gas fireplace, a jetted tub in the master bathroom, fresh paint on the exterior, and a roof that's only 3-4 years old. Other features include a hot-tub hookup and an office! Schedule your showing today!
